studi informasi.

178
00:15:35,001 --> 00:15:36,036
Dia berbicara tentangku?

179
00:15:42,275 --> 00:15:44,211
Ya. Studi Informasi.

180
00:15:45,278 --> 00:15:47,280
Dia juga sponsorku dan...

181
